fields.name: Cumulative New Devices
fields.expression: SUM(MEASURE(`New Devices`)) OVER (ORDER BY `Daily Event Date` ROWS UNBOUNDED PRECEDING)

fields.name: % Active Devices
fields.expression: MEASURE(`Active Devices`) / WINDOW_SUM(MEASURE(`Active Devices`), PARTITION BY [`Daily Event Date`])

filters.name: screen_filter
filters.expression: `Screen` != 'home' AND `Screen` != 'support' AND `Screen` != 'welcome' AND `Screen` != 'welcome-core' AND `Screen` != 'welcomeContainer' AND `Screen` IS NOT NULL

fields.name: devices_returning_pct
fields.expression: MEASURE(`Active Devices`) / WINDOW_SUM(MEASURE(`Active Devices`), PARTITION BY [`Monthly First Device Event Date Time`])
